#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Accounting:</strong> Manage shared expenses, distribute costs by "
"owner, and maintain owner-specific balance sheets."
msgstr ""
"<strong>会計:</strong> 共有費用の管理、所有者ごとの費用配分、各所有者別の貸借"
"対照表の管理を行います。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Automate recurring tasks</strong>, like meter reading imports or "
"expense allocation."
msgstr ""
"たとえば、メーター検針データの取込みや費用配分など<strong>定期的な作業を自動"
"化</strong>します。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>CRM:</strong> Track and manage incoming leads and communications "
"with potential new condominiums."
msgstr ""
"<strong>CRM:</strong> 新規マンションの見込み顧客からの問い合わせ、やり取りを"
"追跡・管理します。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Calendar:</strong> Schedule and organize association meetings, "
"collecting votes during general assemblies and share the report."
msgstr ""
"<strong>カレンダー:</strong> 協会の会議をスケジュールし、組織化します。総会で"
"の投票を集計し、報告書を共有します。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Condominium:</strong> Define buildings, properties, owner and tenant "
"histories, meter readings and distribution keys."
msgstr ""
"<strong>マンション:</strong> 建物、物件、所有者および入居者の履歴、メーター検"
"針、配分キーを定義します。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Contacts:</strong> Manage contacts turning prospects into "
"condominiums, as well as owners, tenants and suppliers."
msgstr ""
"<strong>連絡先:</strong> 見込み客をマンション管理へと移行して管理するととも"
"に、所有者、入居者、仕入先を管理します。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Define a chart of accounts template for condominiums</strong> to "
"save time setting up accounting aspects. Don't hesitate to contact us if "
"needed!"
msgstr ""
"<strong>マンション管理向け勘定科目テンプレートを定義</strong>することで、会計"
"設定にかかる時間を節約できます。必要に応じて、お気軽にお問い合わせください。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Documents App: </strong>Request and share documents."
msgstr "<strong>ドキュメントアプリ:</strong>ドキュメントを申請して共有します。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>In such situation, feel free to experiment with this database and "
"then to create a new one for your own usage.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>このような場合は、まずこのデータベースで自由に操作や実験を行ってみて"
"ください。その後、ご自身の用途に合わせた新しいデータベースを作成することがで"
"きます。</strong>"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Keep contact data up-to-date</strong> to ensure seamless "
"communication during meetings, billing and accounting."
msgstr ""
"<strong>連絡先情報を最新の状態に保ち</strong> 会議、請求、会計業務における円"
"滑なコミュニケーションを確保します。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Leverage tags and filters</strong> in Contacts and CRM to segment "
"your audience (owners, tenants, suppliers, condominiums...)."
msgstr ""
"連絡先とCRMで<strong>タグとフィルタを活用</strong>し、対象者(所有者、テナン"
"ト、サプライヤー、マンション管理組合など)をセグメント化します。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.report_calendar_event_general_meeting_document
msgid "<strong>Motions</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>議案</strong>"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Sales:</strong> Send quotations, confirm orders, and invoice shared "
"expenses to owners."
msgstr ""
"<strong>販売:</strong>見積を送付し、オーダを確定し、共有費用を所有者へ請求し"
"ます。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Sign</strong> <strong>App: </strong>Send digital property "
"reservation contracts."
msgstr ""
"<strong>署名</strong> <strong>アプリ: </strong>デジタル不動産予約契約書を送信"
"します。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Use quotation templates</strong> in the Sales app to standardize "
"quotes and reduce manual errors."
msgstr ""
"<strong>販売アプリ</strong> の見積書テンプレートを使用し、見積書を標準化して"
"手作業によるミスを削減します。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>VoIP Integration:</strong> Organize online meetings directly from "
"Odoo with integrated call capabilities."
msgstr ""
"<strong>VoIP連携:</strong> 通話機能を連携し、Odooから直接オンライン会議を管理"
"できます。"

#. module: condominium
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:condominium.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Website Builder:</strong> Build a professional website with lead "
"capture forms and member areas."
